VY'yN 'aYVB VY'aMUr.
ShM'yV ShMV'y MLThY VThHY-Z'aTh ThNChVMThYKM.
Sh'aVNY V'aNKY 'aDBUr V'aChUr DBUrY ThL'yYG.
H'aNKY L'aDM ShYChY V'aM-MDV'y L'a-ThQTShUr UrVChY.
PhNV-'aLY VHShMV VShYMV YD 'yL-PhH.
V'aM-ZKUrThY VNBHLThY V'aChZ BShUrY PhLTShVTh.
MDV'y UrSh'yYM YChYV 'yThQV GM-GBUrV ChYL.
ZUr'yM NKVN LPhNYHM 'yMM VTSh'aTSh'aYHM L'yYNYHM.
BThYHM ShLVM MPhChD VL'a ShBT 'aLVH 'yLYHM.
ShVUrV 'yBUr VL'a YG'yL ThPhLT PhUrThV VL'a ThShKL.
YShLChV KTSh'aN 'yVYLYHM VYLDYHM YUrQDVN.
YSh'aV KThPh VKNVUr VYShMChV LQVL 'yVGB.
YBLV BTVB YMYHM VBUrG'y Sh'aVL YChThV.
VY'aMUrV L'aL SVUr MMNV VD'yTh DUrKYK L'a ChPhTShNV.
MH-ShDY KY-N'yBDNV VMH-NV'yYL KY NPhG'y-BV.
HN L'a BYDM TVBM 'yTShTh UrSh'yYM UrChQH MNY.
KMH NUr-UrSh'yYM YD'yK VYB'a 'yLYMV 'aYDM ChBLYM YChLQ B'aPhV.
YHYV KThBN LPhNY-UrVCh VKMTSh GNBThV SVPhH.
'aLVH YTShPhN-LBNYV 'aVNV YShLM 'aLYV VYD'y.
YUr'aV 'yYNV KYDV VMChMTh ShDY YShThH.
KY MH-ChPhTShV BBYThV 'aChUrYV VMSPhUr ChDShYV ChTShTShV.
HL'aL YLMD-D'yTh VHV'a UrMYM YShPhVT.
ZH YMVTh B'yTShM ThMV KLV ShL'aNN VShLYV.
'yTYNYV ML'aV ChLB VMCh 'yTShMVThYV YShQH.
VZH YMVTh BNPhSh MUrH VL'a-'aKL BTVBH.
YChD 'yL-'yPhUr YShKBV VUrMH ThKSH 'yLYHM.
HN YD'yThY MChShBVThYKM VMZMVTh 'yLY ThChMSV.
KY Th'aMUrV 'aYH BYTh-NDYB V'aYH 'aHL MShKNVTh UrSh'yYM.
HL'a Sh'aLThM 'yVBUrY DUrK V'aThThM L'a ThNKUrV.
KY LYVM 'aYD YChShK Ur'y LYVM 'yBUrVTh YVBLV.
MY-YGYD 'yL-PhNYV DUrKV VHV'a-'yShH MY YShLM-LV.
VHV'a LQBUrVTh YVBL V'yL-GDYSh YShQVD.
MThQV-LV UrGBY NChL V'aChUrYV KL-'aDM YMShVK VLPhNYV 'aYN MSPhUr.
V'aYK ThNChMVNY HBL VThShVBThYKM NSh'aUr-M'yL.
